<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>StateSide Stitch</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  background: #f6f4f1;
  color: #2f2f2f;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
}

/* NAV */
nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 25px 70px;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  background: rgba(246,244,241,0.9);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  z-index: 10;
}

nav h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 22px;
}

nav ul {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  gap: 30px;
}

nav a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #2f2f2f;
  position: relative;
}

nav a::after {
  content: "";
  height: 1px;
  width: 0%;
  background: #2f2f2f;
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -4px;
  left: 0;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

nav a:hover::after {
  width: 100%;
}

/* HERO */
.hero {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 80px;
  background: #eae7e2;
}

.hero-text {
  animation: fadeUp 1s ease forwards;
}

.hero-text h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 52px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero-text p {
  max-width: 420px;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.buttons button {
  padding: 12px 22px;
  border: 1px solid #2f2f2f;
  background: transparent;
  margin-right: 10px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.buttons button:hover {
  background: #2f2f2f;
  color: white;
}

.hero img {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 6px;
  animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
}

/* FEATURES */
.features {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  padding: 50px;
  text-align: center;
}

.features div {
  max-width: 200px;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(20px);
}

/* PRODUCTS */
.products {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 30px;
  padding: 70px;
}

.card {
  background: white;
  padding: 12px;
  transition: 0.3s;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.card img {
  width: 100%;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

/* STATEMENT */
.statement {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 100px 20px;
}

.statement h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 36px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

/* SPLIT */
.split {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  padding: 80px;
  gap: 60px;
}

.featured {
  border: 1px solid #ddd;
  padding: 20px;
  background: white;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.featured:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.featured img {
  width: 100%;
}

/* EMAIL */
.email {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 60px;
  background: #eae7e2;
}

input {
  padding: 12px;
  width: 260px;
  border: 1px solid #aaa;
}

button.join {
  padding: 12px 18px;
  border: 1px solid black;
  background: transparent;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

button.join:hover {
  background: black;
  color: white;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 30px;
  font-size: 12px;
}

/* ANIMATIONS */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from {opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);}
  to {opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);}
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from {opacity: 0;}
  to {opacity: 1;}
}

/* SCROLL REVEAL */
.reveal {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(40px);
  transition: 1s;
}

.reveal.active {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>
  <h1>StateSide Stitch</h1>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#">Shop</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Process</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-text">
    <h2>Elevated Textiles. Made Here.</h2>
    <p>High-design home essentials crafted in the USA—bringing texture, quality, and intention to everyday living.</p>
    <div class="buttons">
      <button>Shop Collection</button>
      <button>Our Story</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c">
</section>

<section class="features reveal">
  <div><strong>Crafted in the USA</strong><p>Small-batch production.</p></div>
  <div><strong>Design-Forward</strong><p>Texture-rich aesthetics.</p></div>
  <div><strong>Accessible Luxury</strong><p>Boutique feel.</p></div>
  <div><strong>Built to Last</strong><p>High-quality materials.</p></div>
</section>

<section class="products reveal">
  <div class="card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582582494700-8c66e6c0c1d5"><p>Decorative Pillows</p></div>
  <div class="card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616627989237-ff0b02d293b3"><p>Textured Throws</p></div>
  <div class="card"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1583847268964-b28dc8f51f92"><p>Luxury Towels</p></div>
</section>

<section class="statement reveal">
  <h2>Closing the Gap Between Basic and Beautiful</h2>
  <p>We bring elevated design into everyday spaces—without compromise.</p>
</section>

<section class="split reveal">
  <div class="featured">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582582494700-8c66e6c0c1d5">
    <h4>Textured Linen Pillow – Sand</h4>
    <p>$38</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h2>Designed and Crafted in the United States</h2>
    <p>Our domestic manufacturing allows us to move faster, design smarter, and deliver better quality.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="email reveal">
  <p>Be the first to experience the launch.</p>
  <input placeholder="Enter Email">
  <button class="join">Join</button>
</section>

<footer>
  © 2026 StateSide Stitch
</footer>

<script>
const reveals = document.querySelectorAll(".reveal");

window.addEventListener("scroll", () => {
  reveals.forEach(el => {
    const top = el.getBoundingClientRect().top;
    if (top < window.innerHeight - 100) {
      el.classList.add("active");
    }
  });
});
</script>

</body>
</html>
